	", this run is missing basic optimization techniques like 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=jumping off platforms|href=/GameResources/CommonTricks#JumpingOffLedges)
	" to gain higher downward velocity and arrive to the bottom sooner. In Super Mario Bros it's also faster to accelerate by 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=jumping and turning on specific frames|href=/GameResources/NES/SuperMarioBros#AcceleratingFaster)
	". We require 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=speed oriented movies to be technically good|href=/MovieRules#MovieMustBeTechnicallySound)
	", which means it should not be easily improvable by large amounts of time, and all known techniques should be used. To learn more about TASing techniques and all the other relevant aspects, check out our 
	(__wikiLink|href=/TASingGuide|implicitdisplaytext=TASing Guide)
	"!
	$LF
