[div class=p 
	"The second problem is the category choice. "Glitchless" can't go to the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Standard class|href=/MovieRules#Standard)
	" unless 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Major Skip Glitch|href=/MovieTagGuidelines#MajorSkipGlitch)
	" is the only glitch in the game. Sometimes a movie in the Standard class may contain 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=speed/entertainment tradeoffs|href=/MovieTagGuidelines#ContainsSpeedEntertainmentTradeoffs)
